These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, montecristo, baccarat, ritmeester
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, bus, skateboard, van
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not the ritmeester-smoker##6
 5. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the right of the dannemann-smoker##5
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the montecristo-smoker##8
 8. the montecristo-smoker is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
 9. the dannemann-smoker is not the person driving the van##6
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person driving the van##1
11. the montecristo-smoker is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8
12. the montecristo-smoker is in an even position##4
13. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
14. the person driving the skateboard is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Cigar    | dannemann         | ritmeester     | baccarat     | montecristo         |
| Transport   | bus | van    | skateboard     | car |
| Sport   | cycling       | ice-hockey | volleyball | skiing       |

