.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, milk, water
4 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, rat, turtle
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, blend, prince, old-henry
 1. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
 2. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
 3. the prince-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 4. the person drinking water is the owner of the goldfish##1
 5. the owner of the dog is not the person drinking milk##6
 6. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 9. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
10. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | milk          | coffee      | water      | iced-tea   |
| Pet        | rat     | dog | goldfish | turtle      |
| Cigar      | old-henry | blend    | davidoff  | prince |

