.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking, reading, sudoku
City: paris, rome, marseilles, london
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, goldfish, turtle, bird
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
 5. the owner of the rabbit is not the person traveling to paris##6
 6. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 7. the person traveling to paris is not to the right of the person traveling to london##8
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading  | filmmaking | sudoku | card-games |
| City   | rome  | paris      | london | marseilles        |
| Pet     | rabbit | turtle       | bird    | goldfish     |

