.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, horror, mystery, thriller
There 4 different types of food: carrot, raspberry, nectarine, banana
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, security-guard, social-worker, freelancer
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 2. the security-guard is not to the left of the person eating raspberry##8
 3. the person eating banana is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
 4. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the security-guard##8
 6. the social-worker is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
 7. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
 8. the freelancer is somewhere to the right of the security-guard##5
 9. the dressmaker is on the left of the social-worker##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is the social-worker##1
11. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | thriller | horror    | mystery |
| Food   | nectarine    | raspberry     | carrot   | banana     |
| Job   | dressmaker | social-worker   | security-guard | freelancer    |

