 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
 6. the person eating watermelon is not the person driving the motorbike##6
 7. the person driving the train is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
 8. the person eating apricot is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the person eating pomegranate is not to the right of the person driving the train##8
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person driving the motorbike##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the person eating pomegranate##8

.:: Answer ::.
