 4. the blend-smoker is not to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 6. the dannemann-smoker is the owner of the fish##1
 7. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
 8. the tiparillo-smoker is between the person eating blueberry and the dannemann-smoker##2
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the right of the person eating blueberry##8
10. the person eating plum is not to the right of the person eating potato##8
11. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5

.:: Answer ::.
