 4. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 5. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
 6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the polish##6
 8. the person who growslily is not to the right of the polish##8
 9. the polish is not to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
10. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
11. the person who growslily is not to the left of the polish##8
12. the person who growstulip is not to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##8
13. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5

