3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
4. the person who likes fuchsia is not to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
5. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
6. the person eating asparagus is not to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
7. the person eating lime is the person who likes ebony##1
8. the person eating lime is somewhere between the person who likes orange and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
9. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
