.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, magic-tricks, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, cricket, cycling, soccer
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##8
 2. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person who's sport is soccer and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking fanta is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 8. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##8
10. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
11. the person drinking fanta is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
13. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
14. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | drawing    | magic-tricks | woodworking | fishing    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | sprite    | fanta      | almond-milk |
| Sport     | cricket | sailing          | soccer      | cycling       |

