There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, fuchsia, azure, turquise
1. the person who growsdaisy is the person who likes purple##1
2. the colombian is not to the right of the person who likes fuchsia##8
3. the person who likes turquise is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growszinnia##2
4. the canadian is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the colombian is not the person who likes azure##6
6. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the russian##1
7. the person who likes azure is somewhere between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes fuchsia##7
8. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
9. the person who likes azure is the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | colombian | canadian     | russian  | indonesian |
| Flower           | balloon-flower      | zinnia        | poppy   | daisy |
| Color         | fuchsia  | azure | turquise | purple       |

 